my desktop notify project. I need notifiers like one feed (skype, twitter, github and others) on different machines :) 

skype install:

# Setup skype Notifiers in advanced view to run this script
# [absolute path]skype_safe_notify.rb %sskype %smessage

termtter install:

 sudo ln /home/ypetya/project/ruby-desktop-notify/termtter/lib/plugins/say.rb /usr/lib/ruby/gems/1.8/gems/termtter-1.3.0/lib/plugins/say.rb -s
